<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Password Changed</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #4CAF50;">Password Changed Successfully</h1>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Your password has been changed successfully.</p>
    <p>If you didn't make this change, please contact our support team immediately:</p>
    <a href="{{supportUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #FF5722; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      Contact Support
    </a>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Security Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>